text: Nabiyow toysa isi nafsi Islaam diini fan uyfukkun aka diinittek xabanah gacak, amah cakki diiniy koo kah amrisnek, usuk Yallih diiniy Yalli sinam elle giné kinni. Yallih ginóo kee kay diini korissam matan, too diini usuk massal yan diini, kinnih immay maggo mari mayaaxiga usuk cakki diini kinnim
